# News: Powerside

PingThings has singed a memorandum with PowerSide to ensure that microPMUs are integrated with the PingThings analytics platform. This represents a great leap forward for the NI4AI project. Read more here:  (March 29,2022[https://powerside.com/powerside-and-pingthings-sign-memorandum-of-understanding-to-offer-power-quality-solutions-to-enable-transformation-of-the-electrical-grid/](https://powerside.com/powerside-and-pingthings-sign-memorandum-of-understanding-to-offer-power-quality-solutions-to-enable-transformation-of-the-electrical-grid/)
